const faqs = [
  {
    q: "What Electrolux appliances do you repair in Los Angeles?",
    a: "All current Electrolux US categories. Front-load and compact washers (EFLS, EFLW, ECWM series including Perfect Steam variants), gas and electric dryers (EFME, EFMG, ECWM compact), French door and Side-by-Side refrigerators (EI23, EW23, EI28, EW28 series with PureAdvantage water filtration), dishwashers (EIDW and EI24ID series), electric and dual-fuel ranges (EI30, EW30 with PreciseAir convection), wall ovens, and over-the-range microwaves. Our techs service the full residential Electrolux lineup across LA, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside counties. We also service the Electrolux Professional commercial dishwashers separately — different parts chain, different pricing, see the Electrolux Professional dishwasher page if that's what you need."
